SUMMARY:Walk Duke Wall
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nIt’s getting pretty out again and 
 I just want to be outside most evenings. Come join me doing a couple of la
 ps around Duke Wall!\n\nWe’ll meet at the area of the wall acrosss from 
 Sedgefield St. and will set off from there towards N. Buchanan.\n\nThey do
  tow at the Whole Foods\, so I recommend street parking in Trinity Heights
  and walking over.
