SUMMARY:Romance Book Club: Tomorrow And Tomorrow And Tomorrow
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nThe next book we’ll be reading is 
 “Tomorrow And Tomorrow And Tomorrow” by Gabrielle Zevin.\n\nCome join 
 us a Namu as we meet to chat about the book!\n\nI’ll arrive early to fin
 d us a spot and will message in the chat where we’ll be. Can’t wait to
  see everybody!
