SUMMARY:Exchange Family Center Presents: 3rd Annual Bull City Pickleball C
 lassic
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\n***Event is not free***\n(https://ap
 p.pickleballden.com/external-tournament/1647782)\n\nHello everyone\,\n\nIf
  you didn't know when I am not planning events here\, I plan events for wo
 rk\, lol.\n\nThat being said\, the nonprofit I work with and I are hosting
  a fundraiser in the form of a Pickleball tournament! Registration opened 
 this morning and I wanted to get the word out. If you like pickleball or e
 njoy supporting a local Durham charity you should consider entering\, dona
 ting\, or just coming to spectate.\n\nTournament fee is $50\nand each addi
 tional bracket is $10\n\nIf you have any more specific questions\, feel fr
 ee to message me personally or leave a comment!\n\nHope to see you there!\
 n\n##
